School isn't a scam, school is an avenue to expand your social network, and explore the opportunities that come with them later in life. In school, you meet different classes of people. Naturally, you gravitate towards those with like minds and intentions. Being a lone-ranger in school does not augur well for you. No man is an island; no man can succeed without the input of other men. In University campuses, apart from academic activities, there are social clubs and organizations that make room for your all-round growth as a student.

It is just the way you take school seriously will reflect in you